    <h4>Biography</h4>
    <div class='note'>
      <p>Article author for the first issue of Linux Journal <a href="http://www.linuxjournal.com/issue/1" rel="nofollow">http://www.linuxjournal.com/issue/1</a></p>
<p>Fallen out of touch with Linux to some degree &#8212; I&#8217;ve spent time working at both the <span class="caps">IBM</span> and Microsoft evil empires.  Not that I consider them evil, mind you.</p>
<p>Lately working on interesting <span class="caps">USB</span> devices, including cheap <span class="caps">USB</span> terminals to enable lower cost and plug-and-play setup of Linux multiseat configurations.</p>
